{"tid":463773,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃鍶雅上曬報勁有睇頭　揭於16年港姐選舉曾是大熱門","createTime":"2017-11-09T23:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T05:52:13.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad2339429ebc59e5e437f7411d53708a704c935","tid":463773,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T23:50:28.000Z","msg":"近日馬主吳鐵成功跑贏頭馬「鐵胆王」上曬新聞，不過當日大家的焦點不在馬主，亦不在頭馬身上.......各大傳媒的視線全都落在穿上谷胸噴血裝的黃鍶雅身上。黃鍶雅這個名字可能不太記得是誰，但如果我說2016年港姐競選的大熱門，可能你腦海開始浮現一個個面孔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/9ea9f7efae1f1ce198f2e15b86ec5fc6/tumblr_oz13y1hKd11vzwxhdo1_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F9ea9f7efae1f1ce198f2e15b86ec5fc6%2Ftumblr_oz13y1hKd11vzwxhdo1_1280.png&h=981fa003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/e98610ff7e8c18d23cbb6017f521dc0b/tumblr_oz14b2aTKP1vzwxhdo1_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fe98610ff7e8c18d23cbb6017f521dc0b%2Ftumblr_oz14b2aTKP1vzwxhdo1_1280.png&h=10388261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除了冠軍馮盈盈，當年Nicole黃鍶雅都是大熱門！因為她一身健康膚色，外表輪廓深，加上上圍不錯有明顯S形body，又被稱為「翻版高海寧」，憑著弗爆身材及爛玩背景上位。她不時會在Instagram上載火辣比堅尼照益街坊，不過她最後竟然於最後10強被即時叮走淘汰，很多人都大感不解。<br />\n<br />\n小編覺得可能那時候她被爆出曾經爆粗、食水煙、夜店攬仔的歷史吧，對於港姐強調需要有氣質、優雅形象方面不符合，所以即使樣靚身材正仍然10強止步。<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/99c8ae5c80e6bc9e49e052439efefb71/tumblr_oz14zqSFJD1vzwxhdo1_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F99c8ae5c80e6bc9e49e052439efefb71%2Ftumblr_oz14zqSFJD1vzwxhdo1_1280.jpg&h=f06f17fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼常常大show身材，非常誘人，可見她對自己極有信心<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/d50c658ea772aa8ff5bccaa5cec95908/tumblr_oz14k1UIQ61vzwxhdo1_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fd50c658ea772aa8ff5bccaa5cec95908%2Ftumblr_oz14k1UIQ61vzwxhdo1_1280.png&h=09b2bac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/b2ce3f0693d9a7f273246f6b6c9ba220/tumblr_oz14kx7yRU1vzwxhdo1_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fb2ce3f0693d9a7f273246f6b6c9ba220%2Ftumblr_oz14kx7yRU1vzwxhdo1_1280.jpg&h=703880a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/0ac72a79be90304d4a946d9bb1a529d2/tumblr_oz14o4QNOM1vzwxhdo1_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F0ac72a79be90304d4a946d9bb1a529d2%2Ftumblr_oz14o4QNOM1vzwxhdo1_1280.png&h=82b1d31c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/de538e68099191f55041e19db5c1ff99/tumblr_oz14u0qjx01vzwxhdo1_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fde538e68099191f55041e19db5c1ff99%2Ftumblr_oz14u0qjx01vzwxhdo1_1280.jpg&h=bbc9b2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而黃鍶雅本人又不必太過傷心，因為上次都說過，落選佳麗多數都有好發展。既然她有樣有身材，更加年僅22歲，本身於英國倫敦學院修經濟及政治系，亦擁有有米男朋友泰淩醫藥太子爺Andy Ng，數樣加起來早已是人生大贏家，也不需擔心日後的路向了。<br />\n<br />\n▼不但自己及男朋友有錢，經常到處旅遊，連平時穿的衣服都很有公主feel，盡顯氣派<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/bfe8e966656bea25b6aba58ae891b611/tumblr_oz15dabB6g1vzwxhdo1_500.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fbfe8e966656bea25b6aba58ae891b611%2Ftumblr_oz15dabB6g1vzwxhdo1_500.png&h=175de18d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/eae2917efdbfb06cbf4f1a22b9bcf221/tumblr_oz14shdRlU1vzwxhdo1_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Feae2917efdbfb06cbf4f1a22b9bcf221%2Ftumblr_oz14shdRlU1vzwxhdo1_1280.png&h=c0d423e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不知道大家22歲在做甚麼呢，看到她經常公開放閃，又與男方家人出席活動，黃鍶雅這位大美人入豪門之路應該不遠了。<br />\n<br />\n(圖片來源：蘋果日報、香港01)<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.fanpiece.com/purestalker/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E9%BB%83%E9%8D%B6%E9%9B%85%E4%B8%8A%E6%9B%AC%E5%A0%B1%E5%8B%81%E6%9C%89%E7%9D%87%E9%A0%AD-%E6%8F%AD%E6%96%BC16%E5%B9%B4%E6%B8%AF%E5%A7%90%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%9B%BE%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%B1%E9%96%80-c1300841.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.fanpiece.com%2Fpurestalker%2F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2596-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E9%258D%25B6%25E9%259B%2585%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259B%25AC%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%258B%2581%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%259D%2587%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%2596%25BC16%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A7%2590%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2586%25B1%25E9%2596%2580-c1300841.html&d=JhSGDKJ8TmPruShCzyVNv7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=80013438\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.fanpiece.com/purestalker/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E9%BB%83%E9%8D%B6%E9%9B%85%E4%B8%8A%E6%9B%AC%E5%A0%B1%E5%8B%81%E6%9C%89%E7%9D%87%E9%A0%AD-%E6%8F%AD%E6%96%BC16%E5%B9%B4%E6%B8%AF%E5%A7%90%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E6%9B%BE%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%B1%E9%96%80-c1300841.html</a>"},{"pid":"e06877424561ebecd64fa49bd39b490fdadc58ab","tid":463773,"uid":16493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T23:52:41.000Z","msg":"佢未選港姐已經follow緊ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f2a7efa9adf05f7d400bb76d5f0a24b88301ee","tid":463773,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T23:52:43.000Z","msg":"鱔稿？"},{"pid":"b265d1d0da23b166b654a0e205ad80f30b504e5c","tid":463773,"uid":28763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:05:16.000Z","msg":"咁似木偶妹"},{"pid":"cf13a109f2eed49c1c9bdc3feeaf935bc653854a","tid":463773,"uid":91604,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:52:29.000Z","msg":"佢輸係好正常"},{"pid":"b767c594d7a3bfb7f60e0b1fb6673dab300eb266","tid":463773,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:08:40.000Z","msg":"咪又係臭閪"},{"pid":"827623af940bf4c4f15cac08c3c17b69cce86ecb","tid":463773,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:14:31.000Z","msg":"馬到個太子爺想上岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27614aca84277e765ac24666e2018503bf211c4","tid":463773,"uid":16493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬到個太子爺想上岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢本身都係燈飾大王個女"}]}